Class AbstractConsoleResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.oryx.app.serving.AbstractConsoleResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Console, Console, Console

    public abstract class AbstractConsoleResource
extends Object
    Superclass of web resources that contain a small console for a Serving Layer application. It applies a common header and footer around content from subclasses.
